in the Configure New Data Source page for data source type add an option called Excel/CSV files. if user select that option then display the attached page, so that user can upload Excel/Csv file. do not hardcode the Configured Data Sources. once user create a data source then it should be appeared on the screen. initially it should be blank. if the user deletes any data source, it should ask for confirmation once user confirms it should be deleted for that user. it should not be appeared if user refresh the screen.
